cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.CE

This paper discusses techniques for increasing efficiency and reducing energy consumption in data centers, which are typically associated with the field of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). However, the paper also covers topics related to software engineering (cs.SE), control systems (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and computer engineering (cs.CE) in the context of building green data centers. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely candidates for this paper.
